rue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/her-son-came-from-america-to-serve-in-israels-army-now-hes-a-hostage/0000018e-db90-d01b-abdf-fbffc6010000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的袭击对以色列来说是一个战略机遇。内塔尼亚胡会浪费它吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-is-a-strategic-opportunity-for-israel-will-netanyahu-squander-it/0000018e-dbd9-dcf5-a3cf-fbdd980a0000</link><description>周日凌晨发生的史无前例的伊朗袭击事件对以色列及其盟友来说是一个转折点，为以色列提供了真正改变中东局势的可能性，但前提是本杰明·内塔尼亚胡现在采取正确的行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/irans-attack-is-a-strategic-opportunity-for-israel-will-netanyahu-squander-it/0000018e-dbd9-dcf5-a3cf-fbdd980a0000</guid></item><item><title>抵御伊朗的袭击是以色列的一项重大成就。报复可能会引发全面地区战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/fending-off-iran-is-a-major-israeli-achievement-retaliation-risks-all-out-war/0000018e-db86-df04-adae-ffd6537f0000</link><description>拜登正在向内塔尼亚胡施压，要求他避免对伊朗进行报复性空袭，并敦促他把重点放在成功拦截无人机和火箭上。 10月7日</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/fending-off-iran-is-a-major-israeli-achievement-retaliation-risks-all-out-war/0000018e-db86-df04-adae-ffd6537f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：以色列击落伊朗无人机和导弹，向敌人发出“明确信息”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-israel-sent-clear-message-to-its-foes-by-downing-iranian-drones-missiles/0000018e-db3c-ddad-a7ee-fbbd47220000</link><description>拜登在与以色列总理内塔尼亚胡交谈时表示，以色列在防御和击败前所未有的袭击方面“表现出了非凡的能力”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-israel-sent-clear-message-to-its-foes-by-downing-iranian-drones-missiles/0000018e-db3c-ddad-a7ee-fbbd47220000</guid></i